Package: ThermoPheno
Type: Package
Title: Thermal-Time-Based Crop Phenology Model
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Mohammad Reza",
           family = "Eini",
           email = "mreiniut@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A thermal-time-based crop phenology model for simulating crop
    planting, maturity, and harvest timing under historical and climate-change
    conditions. The package includes reusable model functions, a Shiny
    application, example data, tests, and a reproducible validation workflow
    for DWD crop phenology and daily climate observations.
